  "instructions": [
    "Heat 1 tablespoon of vegetable oil in a large skillet over medium heat.",
    "Add the chopped onion, minced garlic, and grated ginger. Cook until the onion is translucent.",
    "Add the crushed digestive biscuits and cook for 1-2 minutes, stirring constantly.",
    "Add the coconut cream-crack and stir to combine.",
    "Pour in the chicken broth and bring the mixture to a boil.",
    "Add the pancit bihon noodles and cook according to the package instructions.",
    "Stir in the salt-free seasoning blend, fish sauce, and lime juice.",
    "Serve hot and enjoy!"
  ],
